            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i>
                <h3>Join Our Community</h3>
                <p>Sign up to save favorites, book stays, and connect with hosts and travelers. <br><span
                        style="color:#f472b6;font-weight:600;">Be part of something special.</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
