    <div class="help-support-section">
        <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i> Help & Support</h2>
        <p>Need assistance or have questions? Our support team is here to help you 24/7.<br>
            Explore our resources or reach out directly for personalized support.</p>
        <div class="help-support-links">
            <a href="mailto:support@tourstay.com" class="help-link"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> Email
                Support</a>
            <a href="#" class="help-link"><i class="fa-solid fa-book"></i> FAQ & Guides</a>
            <a href="#" class="help-link"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i> Live Chat</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-section">
        <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open-text"></i> Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have a question, suggestion, or just want to say hello? Fill out the form below and our team will get back to
            you soon!</p>
        <form class="contact-form" action="/contact" method="post" autocomplete="off">
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i> Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </div>
